### Plotting Coffechain Sales report


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
report %>%
  group_by(Product) %>%
  summarise('Monthly Sales' = list(Sales),
            .groups = "drop") %>%
  gt() %>%
  gt_plt_sparkline('Monthly Sales',
                   same_limit = FALSE)
```

