### Changing from sparkline to sparkbar

Instead of displaying the values as sparklines, we can display them as sparkbars as shown below.


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
reactable(
  report,
  defaultPageSize = 13,
  columns = list(
    Product = colDef(maxWidth = 200),
    `Monthly Sales` = colDef(
      cell = react_sparkbar(
